Project Coordinator Ukraine & Eurasia
• Full coordination and control of Global Point of Sale project implementation in Ukraine & Eurasia;
• Coordinating 6 specialists across the region;
• Managing the process of budgeting and coordination of Point of Sale Materials across markets (Ukraine & Eurasia) in alignment with all Categories (Marketing Leaders);
• Preparation of briefs and communication with agencies for production and logistics of trade equipment and Point of Sales Materials;
• Control of the procurement process for Point of Sales Materials and trade equipment at all stages: briefing, budgeting, production, warehousing, and placement in retail;
• Coordination of initiatives and interventions towards Global KPIs;
• Support of effective implementation of Global goals and priorities in cooperation with 3rd parties;
• Leading communication and timing between Marketing and Trade marketing to deliver all materials for New Product Development point of sale materials & trade equipment production;
• Verification and approval of cost estimation for design services for Ukraine and Eurasia markets;
• Verification and approval of documents and payments between company and 3rd party companies.

Looking forward to developing my project manager skills in IT and being a part of a great team.

